With its holistic approach, Humana is dedicated to improving the health of the communities it serves by making it easy for people to achieve their best health.

CEO

CEO

Title: CEO

After running competitively at Penn State University, Parker joined Nike as one of our first footwear designers back in 1979. And he’s been at the center of Nike innovation ever since.

Title: CEO

He also headed Apple’s Macintosh division and played a key role in the continued development of strategic reseller and supplier relationships, ensuring flexibility in response to an increasingly demanding marketplace.

Title: CEO
